4. What are severe complications from this virus?

@unusual4tune 

Well, Some patients develop

📌 Pneumonia in both lungs, 

📌 Multi-organ failure, 

📌 Severe acutes respiratory syndrome,

📌  Kidney failure 

📌  and in some cases death.
